fields.value: Replication Data for "Twin Births and Maternal Condition" by Bhalotra and Clarke

dsDescriptionValue.value: This dataset is used to generate all results and tables for the paper "Twin Births and Maternal Condition" by Sonia Bhalotra and Damian Clarke (authors in alphabetical order). Analysis from the paper suggests that healthier women and women who engage in more health-seeking behaviours are more likely to give birth to twins in a wide-range of contexts, including among non-IVF users.
